    dc:description "FIGURE 3. Cumella victoriae sp. nov. Holotype immature female A, body, latateral view; B, antennule; C, maxilliped 3; D, pereopod 1; E, pereopod 2; F, pereopod 3; G, pereopod 4; H, pereopod 5; I, left uropod. Scales (In mm): A, 0.1; B, 0.1; C, 0.05; D – H, 0.1; I, 0.05." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/227874/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

